                     /note="Constitutive sigma-70 promoter (P3) of the
                     beta-lactamase gene (bla / AmpR) from pBR322; 70 bp taken
                     from the minus strand of J01749. Drives bla transcription
                     in the direction opposite the conventional pBR322
                     numbering. Suboptimal -35/-10 hexamers give
                     weak-to-moderate constitutive strength."
